  <trk>
    <name>Through the original valley &quot;La combe de l’A&quot;</name>
    <desc>Hike in one of the most original and wildest side valleys of Valais. Highlights are magnificent landscapes, ideal conditions for observing wild animals, fascinating geological features, and inviting mountain huts.</desc>
